data.description: Sellers offering rate buy down with acceptable offer! A must see one level ranch home! Lovely entrance foyer, with three large rooms, and two full baths. Spacious kitchen area with a breakfast bar, New flooring throughout the house. Outside you will find your newly stained deck, Large fenced in yard with newly sewed grass seed. Off street parking is also available! This one level ranch home is a must see! As you enter the home, you will be greeted by a lovely entrance foyer that leads to three large rooms and two full baths. The spacious kitchen area features a breakfast bar and is perfect for entertaining guests. The house has been updated with new flooring throughout, giving it a fresh and modern look.Outside, you will find a newly stained deck that is perfect for relaxing and enjoying the beautiful weather. The large fenced-in yard has been newly sewed with grass seed, making it the perfect place for children and pets to play. Off-street parking is also available, providing convenience and peace of mind.
